{"tid":1260031,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【置頂】updated英文文宣 推灰衣狗上國際","createTime":"2019-06-26T17:39:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T18:21:05.000Z","uid":214984,"like":33,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fddfc2d76c4a65926ed3fea450b194ed293e93","tid":1260031,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:39:01.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Police disguised as protestor tries to lead Hong Kong protestors into charging through police blockade</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nOn Thursday night, 27th of June, a group of peaceful protestors of Hong Kong surrounded the District Police Headquarter. While the group of over thousand protestors has made the agreement not to step over police&rsquo;s blockade surrounding the headquarter; a grey-clothed man tried to talk the protestors into charging through the blockade. The man, not wearing mask like the vast protestors did, used a hoe-like object to hit the chains wrapping the gate; ignoring the objection of all other protestors. <br />\n<br />\nThe man, finding that he failed persuading, made a call. A while later a gate of the headquarter opened and police inside let the man enter. Given the circumstances, the man is very likely a plainclothes police.<br />\n<br />\nThe man was then identified as the person kicking protestors&rsquo; supplies earlier the day.<br />\n<br />\nThis is how shameful Hong Kong police force is. Sending a disguised policeman trying to persuade the peaceful protestors into committing offence, and thus giving the police force the reason to clear out the protestor group.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">We need your attention. Help us on G20.</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://freedomhk.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffreedomhk.net&d=7GYMv7TAV12u%2FDK%2BXNcYJWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=858424d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">freedomhk.net</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O6VFA8D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO6VFA8D.png&h=3c6f2330&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C4Tsf8E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC4Tsf8E.png&h=a2eb66a0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70263842e14fe64fa8d71434bb76f7838bc38324","tid":1260031,"uid":214984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:12.000Z","msg":"如有錯請指正 急急打<br />\n召喚reddit、twitter文宣巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03940e74a8d57408fb08c208b6e8ea688fe6f607","tid":1260031,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb23ac85f926ae3ecbe96e0ab47beef572149959","tid":1260031,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f24915831da00645d81642a744d6c0dafb2361","tid":1260031,"uid":177338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:41:05.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e8d38b3db833b11586585491927c160f58328379","tid":1260031,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:41:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4b8ccec28fbf316b5579192c996147104417a0","tid":1260031,"uid":58671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:41:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4df5db4c981d09fb3d2e5f9bcf72d038538cd3c4","tid":1260031,"uid":214984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T17:41:54.000Z"